Package org.svvrl.goal.cmd

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CommandConfigurator
    This interface defines configurators for commands.
    CommandDescriptor
    This interface defines a descriptor of a command.
    CommandExtension
    This interface is used to extend the commands of GOAL.
    ComplementConstructionExtension
    This interface is used to extend the complementation constructions available in ComplementCommand.
    ComplementConstructionInterface Deprecated.
    Use ComplementConstructionExtension.
    Expression
    An Expression provides an interface of expressions in GOAL scripts.
    GameSolverExtension
    This interface defines a command-line plugin for game solvers.
    GameSolverInterface Deprecated.
    Use GameSolverExtension.
    GeneratorExtension
    This interface defines generators available in GenerateCommand.
    Statement
    A statement is a block of expressions containing control flows.

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    BreakException
    A BreakException is thrown by a BreakStmt initially can should be handled by ForStmt and WhileStmt.
    ComplementCommand.UnknownResultException  
    ContinueException
    A ContinueException is thrown by a ContinueStmt initially can should be handled by ForStmt and WhileStmt.
    EvaluationException
    An evaluation exception is thrown if there is a problem in evaluating a command-line statement or expression.
